K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:41b-25: bram zes kyang bram ze mo la smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:41b-26: gang gi tshe kho bo de ltar na bar gyur pa na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:41b-27: khyod dang bus yal bar bor ba de'i tshe na bu mo 'dis sman dang g-yog gis legs par gsos par kho bos shes kyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:41b-28: de'i phyir gal te 'di la mkho ba stob par byed na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:41b-31: kho bos 'di khyim bdag mor bzhag cing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:41b-33: bram ze mo de skrag ste bsam pa; bram ze 'di gtum pas gal te de ltar ma byas na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:41b-34: de ltar byed par 'gyur ba'i gnas yod do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:41b-35: snyam du rig nas des smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:41b-37: khyod kyis bu mo mngag gzhug ma la dga' mgur spyad pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-0: @42a *// khye'u 'di khyod kyi sras lags par yang bdag gis ma 'tshal te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-1: da slan chad cung zad kyang mtho 'tsham par mi bgyid do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-2: khye'u de chos zangs su bcug pas de'i ming chol zangs pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-3: chol zangs pa zhes bya bar chags so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-5: chol zangs pa la 'di'i mas bdag gis g-yog byas shing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-6: 'di yang bdag las byung ba yin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-7: snyam pas shin tu byams pa dang ldan par gyur te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-8: de de dang lhan cig gcig tu za zhing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-9: gang du mgron du bos par 'gro ba der yang de dang lhan cig 'gro'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-10: ji tsam dus gzhan zhig na bram ze de yang na bar gyur nas de rtsa ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-14: 'bras bu'i sman dag gis gso bar byed de /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-16: na ba kho nar gyur nas gang gi tshe de 'chi ba la thug pa'i tshor ba byung zhing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-17: ring por mi thogs par dus byed par 'gyur ba de'i tshe na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-18: des bu thu bo nyi zla bkug ste smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-21: mya ngan bya ba ma yin gyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-22: khyod kyi nu bo chol zangs pa 'di mya ngan bya bar 'gyur bas khyod kyis 'di la mkho ba bstab par bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-24: bsags pa kun gyi mtha' 'dzad cing //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-25: mthon po rnams kyi mtha' ltung 'gyur //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-27: gson pa'i mtha' ni 'chi ba yin //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42a-28: zhes bya ba yin pas de dus kyi chos dang ldan par gyur nas de /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-0: nyi zla dang chol zangs pa dang snying du sdug cing 'brel ba'i rtsa lag gzhan dag gis dur khrod du khyer te bsregs @42b nas de'i 'og tu mya ngan sangs pa byas te 'khod do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-1: ji tsam dus gzhan zhig na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-2: nyi zlas zan gyi dus su chol zangs pa tshur shog /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-3: 'dir zan zo zhig ces bos pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-6: khyod bran mo'i bu dang ji ltar lhan cig zan za bar byed /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-8: bdag gis dus thams cad du nu bo 'di dang lhan cig zos shing 'thungs na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-9: da ji ltar bran mo'i bu zhes bya /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-12: khyod kyi pha gtum par gyur pas de la cung zad smra bar sus nus /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-14: bran mo'i bu kho na yin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-15: chol zangs pas thos nas de ma'i gan du song ste smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-17: bdag bran mo'i bu yin pa bden nam /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-20: rang gi las kyi 'bras bu la spyod pa yin pas su zhig su'i bran yin /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-22: yul gzhan du song la thos pa 'dzin cing 'dug cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-23: de yul gzhan du song nas de yul gzhan du rang gi ming chol zangs pa zhes bya ba btang ste zla ba zhi ba zhes bya bar bsgrags nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-24: ji tsam na mthar gyis mnyan yod du phyin nas de na bram ze mdun na 'don zhig 'dug nas de gcig nas gcig tu de'i gan du song ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-26: spyod lam zhi bas gus par smra bar byas te mtha' gcig tu 'dug go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-29: zhes bya ba'i tshig kun tu brjod pas rab tu dga' bar byas te dris pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-33: khyod kyis rdo 'jog na 'khod pa'i skye bo'i tshogs dag shes sam /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:42b-35: de nas bram ze zla grags de'i gtam ci grags /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43a-1: ze'i khye'u nges ngu bar brtsams pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43a-5: de bdag gi pha lags so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43a-9: skyes pas na gdon mi za bar 'chi bar bya dgos kyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43a-10: kho bo khyod kyi pha'i chung grogs yin gyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43a-11: bag phobs shig dang thams cad bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43a-14: re zhig bgyi ba gzhan btang ste je rig byed bklag par bgyi'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43a-17: bram ze rang gi rigs sgrog pas bya ba ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43a-19: des de'i drung du rig byed bklag par brtsams pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43a-23: des dus cung zhig gis rig byed bzhi po dag bklags so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43a-24: bram ze de mngon par dga' nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43a-25: des de'i bu mo rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43a-26: de'i chung mar byin zhing bdag dbang ba'i nor mang po dag kyang byin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43a-27: de bram ze mdun na 'don gyi mag par gyur cing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43a-28: rig byed bzhi dang ldan pa zhes 'jig rten thams cad la rnam par grags shing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43a-31: bsnyen bkur dag gis khyim gyi 'byor pa nye bar bsags par gyur to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43a-32: ji tsam dus gzhan zhig na rdo 'jog na gnas pa'i skye bo'i tshogs dag zong thogs te mnyan yod du lhags nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43a-33: de dag gi chol zangs pa ji ltar bram ze mdun na 'don gyi mag par gyur cing rig byed bzhi dang ldan pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-0: bsnyen bkur dag gis khyim gyi 'byor pa @43b nye bar bsags par gyur pa thos so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-1: thos nas kyang gros bya bar brtsams pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-2: bdag cag 'dong zhing de mngon sum du byas te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-3: rdo 'jog na nyi zla bde ba'i gtam bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-5: de dag de'i gan du dong ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-6: de dag gis de ngo shes nas cang ma smras par de nas zong bsgyur te rin blangs nas rdo 'jog tu dong /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-7: de dag gis lam gyis ngal ba bsos te nyi zla la smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-8: mnyan yod na khyod kyi nu bo chol zangs pa bram ze mdun na 'don gyi mag par gyur cing rig byed bzhi dang ldan par 'jig rten thams cad la rnam par grags te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-11: bsnyen bkur dag gis khyim gyi 'byor pa nye bar bsags par gyur to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-12: de yid dga' ba skyes nas ma la smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-14: chol zangs pa de mnyan yod na bram ze mdun na 'don gyi mag par gyur cing rig byed bzhi dang ldan par 'jig rten thams cad la grags te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-17: bsnyen bkur dag gis khyim gyi 'byor pa nye bar bsags zhes grag go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-21: bran mo'i bu de la su zhig sbyin pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-23: bsnyen bkur dag gis bsnyen bkur byed par 'os na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-24: de la bsnyen bkur byed par 'gyur /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-25: de nas de cang mi smra bar 'dug go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-26: ji tsam dus gzhan zhig na nyi zla longs spyod bsrabs par gyur nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-29: nu bo de'i gan du song zhig dang gal te na de khyod la longs spyod dag gis bgo bsha' byed par 'gyur ro //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:43b-32: de'i tshe na de bran mo'i bu yin na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-4: gal te de ltar na yang song la de las blang ba ma zlog cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-5: de mas nan gyis mnan pa na don 'thun btsal te mnyan yod du song ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-6: chol zangs pas ji ltar bdag gi phu bo nyi zla de don 'thun pa dang lhan cig 'dir 'ongs te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-7: phyogs ga ge mo zhig na 'dug go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-9: thos nas kyang bsu nas des de la 'ongs pa legs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-10: zhes bya ba'i tshig gis kun tu spyad nas smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-11: bdag gis 'dir zla bzhi ba zhes bya ba'i ming btags kyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-12: bdag la khyod chol zangs pa zhes ma 'bod cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-14: khyod zla ba zhi ba yin na su zhig gzhan du 'bod par 'gyur /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-15: des nyi zla khyim du khrid de bkur sti chen pos mkhos su phab nas zan byin te bram ze mo la smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-18: kho bo'i phu bo nyi zla zhes bya ba yin gyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-19: khyod kyis 'di la mkho ba thams cad bstab par bya zhing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-21: rtag tu gus pa dang bcas par gyis shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-24: des shing 'grogs na bde ba yin la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-28: de chung ma de la nyes pa cung zad tsam gyis kyang khu tshur dang thal lcag dag gis rdeg par byed do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-29: bram ze mo des nyi zla la smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-31: khyed gnyis nu ma gcig la gsol gsol ba'i mched lags na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-32: gang gi slad du khyod ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44a-33: des shing 'grogs na bde ba lags la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-0: @44b gtum zhing gzu lum dang drag shul can lags pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-4: 'dis khyim gyi rig pa ma bklags so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-6: bdag la khyim gyi rig pa de stsol cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-7: nyi zlas tshigs su bcad pa smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-8: rig pas su la'ang sbyin bya min //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-9: rig dang bcas te 'chi bar bya //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-10: rig pa rig dang gus pa dang //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-11: nor gyis sbyin par bya ba yin //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-14: nor ji tsam gyis stsol bar mdzad /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-16: karsha pa na lnga brgyas so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-17: des karsha pa na lnga brgya thogs te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-18: de'i rkang pa gnyis la gtugs nas smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-20: khyim gyi rig pa de stsol cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-23: je kho bo rdzongs shig dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-25: bram ze mo de khyim thab kyi gan du song ste smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-27: khyod kyi gcen 'di khyim gyi bya ba sems pas mi dga' bar 'gyur gyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-32: khyod kyis je 'di'i lam rgyags sta gon gyis shig dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-33: kho bos don 'thun btsal bar bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-34: des rdo 'jog tu 'gro ba'i don 'thun btsal bar brtsams nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-35: bram ze mo des de'i lam rgyags sta gon byas nas karsha pa na lnga brgya thogs te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-36: nyi zla'i rkang pa gnyis la gtugs nas smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-38: khyod brdzang ba'i dus 'di lags kyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-39: khyim gyi rig pa de stsol cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-42: gang gi tshe zla ba zhi pa khyod la rdeg par byed pa de'i tshe khyod kyis rig pa 'di bklag par bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-43: skye bo mang po gzhan dag dang //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:44b-44: gzhan gyis khyim du'ang shes gyur cing //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45a-2: kha rog 'dug cig chol zangs pa //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45a-5: de la gal te rdeg par byed na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45a-9: gsang sngags kyi tshig don dang ldan pa 'di dag ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45a-10: brjod pa tsam kho nas 'bras bu dang bcas par 'gyur ba yin gyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45a-11: phyis 'gyod par mi 'gyur bar legs par zungs shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45a-12: bram ze mo des yi ge de dag legs par bzung nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45a-13: zla ba zhi pas kyang rdo 'jog tu 'gro ba'i don 'thun btsal nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45a-14: nyi zla la karsha pa na dag gis bgo bsha' byas te lam rgyags byin nas de skyel du song ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45a-17: gsang sngags kyi tshig 'di dag bden nam rdzun pa sad par bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45a-19: des zla ba zhi bas nyi zla bskyal te phyir log pa'i tshe bza' ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45a-21: khrus bya ba ci yang sta gon ma byas so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45a-22: de nas zla bzhi pas smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45a-24: chu khyer te shog khrus bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45a-27: chab sta gon ma bgyis so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45a-33: de yang sta gon ma bgyis so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45a-35: nga'i phu bo 'dug pa'i tshe na ngas re zhig khyod btang snyoms su bzhag par zad kyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45a-37: ma brdegs kyi bar du byed du mi btub pa yin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45a-38: zhes des bsnun par gzas te rdeg par brtsams pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-1: khyim gyi rig pa je gsan par bgyi'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-5: skye bo mang po gzhan dag dang //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-6: gzhan gyi khyim du'ang shes gyur cing //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-7: grong srung gis kyang shes gyur gyi //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-8: kha rog 'dug cig chol zangs pa //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-12: smras pa de'i don ci yin /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-14: gal te rdeg par mdzad na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-15: don yang khyod la brjod par bgyi'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-16: de ri dvags gnad du phog pa ltar zug rngus zug nas smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-18: thong la don ma smra zhig ces zer ro //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-20: de'i tshe de'i dus na bram ze zla grags zhes bya ba gang yin pa de ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-22: de'i tshe de'i dus na chol zangs pa zhes bya ba gang yin pa de ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-25: de'i tshe yang 'dis bram ze dang khyim bdag des pa des pa dag gi mdun du nga nye dur brjod cing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-27: rnam par smra ba byas so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-28: da ltar yang 'dis tshangs pa mtshungs par spyod pa des pa des pa rnams kyi mdun du nga nye dur brjod cing /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-29: bdag nyid smra ba dang rnam par smra bar byed do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-32: nga la nye dur brjod pa rnams kyis tshangs pa mtshungs par spyod pa gnas brtan rnams dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-34: gsar bu rnams la yang gus pa dang bcas pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-35: rje sa dang bcas pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-36: 'jigs pa dang bcas pa'i dbang du gyur pa dag gis gnas par bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:45b-37: bka' blo mi bde ba'i dge 'dun lhag ma ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:46a-3: bdag gis dge 'dun lhag ma'i chos bcu gsum po dag bton zin to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:46a-5: ltung ba dang po bdag nyid kyis so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:46a-7: lan gsum gyi bar gyis so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:46a-8: dge slong gis de dag las ltung ba gang yang rung ba zhig byas la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:46a-9: ji srid du shes bzhin du 'chab par byed pa de srid du des mi 'dod bzhin du spo ba bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:46a-10: dge slong gis mi 'dod bzhin du spo ba byas nas 'og tu zhag drug gi bar du dge 'dun mgu bar bya ba spyad par bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:46a-11: dge slong gis mgu bar bya ba spyad nas dbyung ba la thogs te chos dang mthun par byas la /

K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:263b-17: bdag cag gis dge slong drug cu'i zla ba gsum gyi bsod snyoms ma phul lam /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:263b-19: dge slong dag lhags par gyur nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:263b-20: de dag gis dbyar gyi nang nyid du thams cad zos te dong ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:263b-21: khyed gnyis kyis dge slong gang dag khrid de 'ongs /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:263b-24: khyed gnyis rgya mtsho chen por dong nas nor bu mching bu dag khyer te 'ongs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:263b-25: de na dge slong gzhan dag med dam /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:263b-26: ci na drug sde dag khrid de 'ongs /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:263b-27: de dag sh'akya'i bu'i dge sbyong rnams kyi dge sbyong gi tshul ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:263b-32: bdag cag gi dad pa'i myu gu skyes ma thag tu bcom mo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-2: kha zer bar byed pa'i skabs de /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-3: dge slong rnams kyis bcom ldan 'das la gsol to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-4: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis byung ba 'di dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-6: skabs 'di la dge slong gi dge 'dun bsdu ba mdzad do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-7: zhes bya ba la sogs pa snga ma bzhin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-8: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-9: mkhyen bzhin du rmed par mdzad pa ste zhes bya ba la sogs pa yang snga ma bzhin te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-10: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyis dge slong drug sde dag la rmas pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-12: khyed kyis dbyar gyi rnyed pa dbyar gyi nang du bgos pa bden nam /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-15: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyis dge sbyong gi tshul ma yin pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-16: rjes su mthun pa ma yin pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-18: tshul dang mthun pa ma yin pa de ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-19: rab tu byung bas bya ba ma yin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-20: zhes rnam par smad par mdzad do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-21: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis rnam grangs du mas rnam par smad nas dge slong rnams la bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-24: phan yon bcu yang dag par gzigs pas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-25: 'dul ba la nyan thos rnams kyi bslab pa'i gzhi bca' bar bya ste zhes bya ba la sogs pa snga ma bzhin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-26: 'dul ba la nyan thos rnams kyis bslab pa'i gzhi 'di ltar gdon par bya ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264a-28: dge slong rnams kyis dbyar gyi rnyed par dbyar gyi nang du bgo bar mi bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264b-0: dge slong @264b rnams kyis dbyar gyi rnyed par dbyar gyi nang du 'god par byed na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264b-2: zhes bcom ldan 'das kyis 'dul ba la nyan thos rnams kyi bslab pa'i gzhi de ltar bca' bar mdzad do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264b-3: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das mnyan yod na rgyal byed tshal mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264b-4: mnyan yod na dge slong ma skye rgu'i bdag mo chen mo go'u ta mi dang chos sbyin gnyis las skye rgu'i bdag mo chen mo go'u ta mi ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264b-6: 'khor yang spong ba ma dang ldan pa yin la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264b-9: 'khor yang mdo sde'i mtha' pa dang ldan pa yin te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264b-10: de gnyis dbyar khang gcig tu dbyar gnas par khas blangs nas gang gi tshe skye rgu'i bdag mo chen mo go'u ta mi'i 'khor rnam par langs par gyur pa de'i tshe na chos sbyin gyis rang gi 'khor la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264b-12: bcom ldan 'das dge slong rnams la rab tu 'byung ba dang rdzogs par bsnyen pa dge slong ma'i dngos po rjes su gnang ba gang yin pa de thams cad /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264b-13: skye rgu'i bdag mo chen mo go'u ta mi la brten pa yin la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264b-14: bcom ldan 'das kyis kyang gzhan gyi sems srung ba'i gang zag ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264b-15: bsod nams mang du bskyed par byed do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264b-17: khyed cag kyang re zhig mi rtag pa nyid yid la bya ba sgoms shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:264b-19: de dag kyang mi rtag pa nyid yid la bya ba sgom par rtsom mo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265a-0: gang gi tshe chos sbyin gyi 'khor rnam par langs par gyur pa de'i tshe na skye @265a *//
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265a-1: rgu'i bdag mo go'u ta mi yang rang gi 'khor la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265a-3: bcom ldan 'das kyis bskal pa grangs med pa gsum gyis dka' ba spyod pa brgya stong phrag du ma dag gis pha rol tu phyin pa drug yongs su rdzogs par mdzad de /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265a-4: bla na med pa'i mkhyen pa thugs su chud pa gang yin pa de dag thams cad /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265a-5: sems can la phan pa'i rgyu yin la /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265a-6: bcom ldan 'das kyis kyang gzhan gyi sems srung ba'i gang zag ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265a-7: bsod nams mang po skyed par byed do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265a-9: khyed cag kyang re zhig mi rtag pa nyid dang ldan pa'i mdo sde'i mtha' dag kha ton gyis shig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265a-11: de dag kyang mi rtag pa nyid dang ldan pa'i mdo sde'i mtha' dag kha ton byed par rtsom mo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265a-13: de ltar phan tshun sems rjes su srung bas dge ba'i chos rnams kyis mi 'phel te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265a-14: chu med pa nas autpa la bzhin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265a-15: chos sbyin la dge bsnyen sa ga zhes bya ba mngon par dad pas des yo byad thams cad kyis de mgron du bos so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265a-16: dus gzhan zhig na dge bsnyen sa ga chos sbyin gyi rkang pa la phyag 'tshal du 'ongs pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265a-17: chos sbyin gyis de la smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265a-19: dge slong ma rab tu mang po dag dbyar khang gcig tu dbyar gnas par khas blangs pa de dag phan tshun sems rjes su srung bas dge ba'i chos rnams kyis mi 'phel te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265a-20: chu med pa nas autpa la bzhin du gyur na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265b-0: khyod kyis dge slong ma'i dge 'dun gyi phyir dbyar @265b khang byed du 'jug nus sam /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265b-3: bdag la karsha pa na dag ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265b-5: sa gzhi rgyal po dbang bas sa gzhi'i slad du rgyal po la gsol ba mdzod cig dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265b-6: der bdag gis dbyar khang bgyid du stsal to //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265b-7: dge slong ma chos sbyin btsun mo phreng ldan ma'i gan du song ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265b-8: btsun mo phreng ldan mas smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265b-11: 'phags ma sku don ci zhig gi slad du byon /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265b-12: bdag dge slong ma'i dbyar khang zhig bgyid du stsol bar 'tshal na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265b-13: sa gzhi rgyal po mnga' bas sa gzhi'i slad du rgyal po la gsol ba bgyi bar 'tshal lo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265b-15: bdag gis 'phags ma'i slad du lha la gsol bar bgyi'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265b-17: btsun mo phreng ldan ma ko sa lar byung ba'i rgyal po gsal rgyal gyi gan du song ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265b-20: khyod kyi pho brang du 'phags ma chos sbyin byon par gyur pa ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265b-21: khyod kyis rnyed pa legs par rnyed do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265b-23: de dge slong ma'i dbyar khang zhig bgyid du stsol bar bzhed na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265b-24: dog sa rgyal po mnga' bas dog sa'i slad du rgyal po la gsol bar bgyid ces mchi'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265b-26: gal te 'phags ma chos sbyin re zhig gnas 'di nyid bzhed na yang de 'di nyid du bzhugs la rag ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265b-27: nga'i pho brang gzhan du byed du gzhug go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:265b-29: gang du dgyes pa der dbyar khang bgyid du stsol la rag go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266a-0: btsun mo phreng ldan mas chos sbyin la lhas 'phags ma la dam pa @266a *//
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266a-2: gal te 'phags ma chos sbyin gnas 'di nyid bzhed na yang de 'di nyid du bzhugs la rag ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266a-3: nga'i pho brang gzhan du byed du gzhug go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266a-4: gal te mi bzhed na; gang du dgyes pa der dbyar khang bgyid du stsal la rag ces byung ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266a-6: chos byin gyis dge bsnyen sa ga la ko sa lar byung ba'i rgyal po gsal rgyal gyis bdag la dam pa byin te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266a-7: gal te 'phags ma chos sbyin re zhig gnas 'di nyid bzhed na yang de 'di nyid du bzhugs la rag ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266a-8: nga'i pho brang gzhan du byed du gzhug go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266a-10: gang du dgyes pa der dbyar khang bgyid du stsal la rag ces byung ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266a-12: ko sa lar byung ba'i rgyal po gsal rgyal la ral gri'i mthu can dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266a-13: rgyal rigs bzang po pa zhes bya ba'i khrom gnyis yod pa las /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266a-14: ral gri'i mthu can gyi khrom dmag gi gnas su song ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266a-15: de dag gi chung ma rnams skyes pa gzhan dag dang lhan cig dga' mgur spyod par byed pas phyogs de go skabs dben par gyur nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266a-17: phyogs 'dir dbyar khang byed du chug cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266a-18: dge bsnyen sa gas phyogs der dbyar khang byed du bcug nas /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266a-19: dge slong ma rnams kyi der gnas par brtsams so; ;ral gri'i mthu can gyi khrom de dmag gi gnas nas phyir 'ongs te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266a-20: de dag gis chung ma de dag bkug cing bkug cing brdeg par brtsams pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266a-21: srang dag na de dag ngu ba'i sgra rta'i skad dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-0: @266b glang po che'i skad lta bu'i skad mthon po dang skad chen po dag byung ngo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-1: dge slong ma rnams kyis smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-2: 'phags ma bdag cag dgung char gyis 'jigs pas dang la kha'i 'og tu zhugs so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-5: kha cig la dge ba'i rtsa ba yod dam snyam du bsam na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-7: su la rag lus snyam du bsam na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-8: bdag nyid la rag lus par mthong nas des smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-10: gdul ba la ltos pas thams cad bzod par bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-11: chos sbyin gyis phyogs gcig tu gyo mo gsar pa bzhag ste dge slong ma rnams la smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-13: khyed cag gang la sder lhag yod pa de thams cad gyo mo 'dir chug cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-14: de dag la sngar lhag ci yod pa de thams cad gyo mo der 'jug par byed do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-15: de nas byis pa dag der 'ongs par gyur nas chos sbyin gyis de ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-16: khye'u gang dag yin pa de dag la ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-17: 'bru mar byin nas gcig gis gcig gi mgo skud du bcug ste /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-18: rang gi lag gis bca' ba dag sbyin par byed do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-19: bu mo gang dag yin pa de dag la ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-20: bdag nyid kyi 'bru mar gyis mgo bskus nas rang gi lag gis bca' ba dag sbyin par byed do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-21: byis pa de dag gis de dag khyer te rang rang gi khyim dag tu dong ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-22: de dag gi ma dag gis dris pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-23: khyed cag la 'di dag sus byin /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-26: chung ma de dag gis bsam pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:266b-29: bdag cag la ma ma'i bya ba mdzad do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267a-1: rig nas de la mngon par dad par gyur te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267a-3: gang gi tshe bdag cag gis khyim thab dag dmag gi gnas su 'dong ba de'i tshe na bdag cag gis khyim thab dag bskyal nas 'phags ma chos sbyin la bsnyen bkur bya'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267a-5: dus gzhan zhig na de dag gi khyim thab dag dmag gi gnas su 'phags pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267a-6: chos sbyin gyis de dag gdul ba'i dus shes nas gtsug lag khang chag chag btab /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267a-8: lci ba gsar pa'i byugs pas bskus te 'dag rdzas dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267a-13: pog phor bzhag nas dge slong ma skad snyan pa dag bskos te bsdad pa dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267a-14: chung ma de dag kyang khyim thab dag bskyal te chos sbyin gyi drung du lhags nas chos sbyin gyis de dag la 'dag rdzas dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267a-15: lag pa bsnyal ba'i chu dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267a-19: pog phor dag byin nas tshigs su bcad pa'i skad kyis mchod rten la phyag 'tshal te dge slong ma'i dge 'dun gyi gong du stan bshams pa nyid la 'dug go /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267a-20: de dag kyang de'i rkang pa la phyag 'tshal te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267a-21: chos mnyan pa'i phyir mdun du 'khod do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267a-22: chos sbyin gyis de dag gi bsam pa dang bag la nyal dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267a-24: rang bzhin khong du chud nas ci nas kyang de dag gis 'jig tshogs la lta ba'i ri'i rtse mo nyi shu mtho ba /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-0: ye shes kyi rdo rjes bcom ste rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras @267b bu mngon sum du byas pa de ltar chos bstan pa byas so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-1: de dag gis bden pa mthong nas smras pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-3: bdag cag gis dge ba'i bshes gnyen 'phags ma la brten nas 'phags mas bdag cag la gang mdzad pa 'di lta bu ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-4: bdag cag la phas kyang ma bgyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-7: lha rnams kyis kyang ma bgyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-8: sngon gyi pha mes rnams kyis kyang ma bgyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-9: dge sbyong dang bram ze dag gis kyang ma bgyis /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-10: byams pa dang mdza' bshes dang rtsa lag gi tshogs kyis kyang ma bgyis te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-11: khrag dang mchi ma'i rgya mtsho ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-13: rus pa'i ri dag las ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-15: ngan song gi sgo dag ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-17: mtho ris dang thar pa'i sgo dag ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-23: lha dang mi rnams kyi nang du ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-27: thog ma ma mchis pa'i dus nas bsags pa'i 'jig tshogs la lta ba'i ri'i rtse mo nyi shu mtho ba /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-28: ye shes kyi rdo rjes bcom ste rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-31: mngon par zhugs pa lags so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-35: dge slong gi dge 'dun la skyabs su mchi'i /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-36: bdag cag dge bsnyen mar gzung du gsol /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:267b-37: deng slan chad ji srid 'tsho'i bar du glo ba thag pa nas skyabs su mchi'o //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:268a-0: de dag mngon par dad par gyur nas khyim khyim du @268a *//
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:268a-1: dong ste khyim chag chag btab /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:268a-3: lci ba gsar pa'i byugs pas bskus te spyod lam zhi bas 'khod do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:268a-4: de dag gi khyim thab dag dmag gi gnas nas phyir 'ongs pa na bsam pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:268a-5: bdag cag gi chung ma glang po che 'tsho ba'am /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:268a-7: su zhig dang lhan cig dga' mgur spyod par byed cing 'dug snyam mo //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:268a-8: de dag gis bdag cag gi khyim thab dag 'ongs zhes thos so //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:268a-9: thos nas kyang bshes pa'i tshig gis rje'i sras dag /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:268a-12: zhes bsus nas de dag rang rang gi khyim du dong ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:268a-13: de dag rang rang gi chung ma dag gis bsku mnye dang dril phyi byas te khrus byas nas lag pas bskus te zas byin no //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:268a-15: 'di dag gi spyod lam 'di lta bu ni /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:268a-17: snyam nas de dag la dris pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:268a-19: khyod kyi spyod lam 'di lta bu 'di sngon ma byung ba yin na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:268a-23: 'phags ma chos sbyin gyis bdag cag la ci nas kyang bdag cag 'khor ba na 'khor ba rnams slan chad nyon mongs pa de lta bu kun tu 'byung bar mi 'gyur ba de ltar chos bstan pa mdzad do //
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:268a-26: ma dul ba 'dul bar mdzad pa yin te /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-006-001:268a-27: des 'di dag btul ba lta ste /
